OL,6,FA paddleboard tour company owner has
OL,7,Fappeared in court charged in
OL,8,Fconnection with the deaths of four
OL,9,Fpeople in 2021.
OL,11,FNerys Bethan Lloyd, 39, from Aberavon,
OL,12,Fappeared before Haverfordwest
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court charged with four
OL,14,Fcounts of gross negligence
OL,15,Fmanslaughter and one offence under the
OL,16,FHealth and Safety at Work Act.
