OL,3,CWoman appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FThe charges relate to an incident on
OL,7,Fthe River Cleddau in Pembrokeshire on
OL,8,F30 October, 2021, which resulted in
OL,9,Fthe deaths of Paul O'Dwyer, 42, Andrea
OL,10,FPowell, 41, Morgan Rogers, 24, and
OL,11,FNicola Wheatley, 40.
OL,13,FLloyd was the owner and sole director
OL,14,Fof Salty Dog Co Ltd, which organised
OL,15,Fthe paddleboarding tour. There were
OL,16,Ffour survivors of the incident.
