OL,3,CWoman appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FDuring her court appearance, she spoke
OL,7,Fonly to confirm her name, date of
OL,8,Fbirth and address during a short
OL,9,Fhearing at the court on Tuesday, 3
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Mark Layton said
OL,13,Fmembers of the families of those who
OL,14,Fdied had attended the court in person
OL,15,Fand online.
OL,17,FHe told them: "I take this opportunity
OL,18,Fto offer my condolences to you for
OL,19,Fyour very sad loss."
