OL,3,CWoman appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FSpeaking to Lloyd, the judge said:
OL,7,F"Your case is one that cannot be dealt
OL,8,Fwith by this court. The date you will
OL,9,Fappear before Swansea Crown Court is
OL,10,FJanuary 3 at 9.30am. You are released
OL,11,Fon unconditional bail."
OL,13,FNo details of the case were given to
OL,14,Fthe court.
OL,16,FDyfed-Powys Police received a call at
OL,17,F9.02am on 30 October, 2021, stating
OL,18,Fthere were a number of paddleboarders
OL,19,Fin distress at the weir in the centre
OL,20,Fof Haverfordwest.
