OL,3,CWoman appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmanslaughter of four paddleboarders
OL,6,FSpeaking at the time, Rosemary
OL,7,FAinslie, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService, said: "The charges relate to
OL,9,Fa commercial paddleboarding river tour
OL,10,Fon October 30 2021, where four of the
OL,11,Fgroup became trapped in Haverfordwest
OL,12,Ftown weir and tragically lost their
OL,13,Flives.
OL,15,F"The Crown Prosecution Service reminds
OL,16,Fall concerned that criminal
OL,17,Fproceedings against the defendant are
OL,18,Factive and that she has the right to a
OL,19,Ffair trial.
